// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1618 — Mass File Rename (killsec)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bea88168-4d47-5ea3-98bc-2defa3093938

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
